c: 3
v: 36
t: "Mana shingalayebula, yaboola mbu; “Nyasaye wanje omulesi esie ndibule weshikhaana- ne Nyasaye amanyile muno shiayebula- Ne weshisiaani shali shinga oweshikhaana tawe. Ne esie emukulishe mbu Mariamu. Esie emushinga khwiwe, nende ulwibulo lulwe ,obaliinde okhurulana nende Shetani owatsubwa"